                                      &= \dfrac {125 \times 234} {100} \\\\
                                      &= \dfrac {29250} {100} \\\\
                                      &= 292.5 \ \text{cm}
\end{aligned}
$

Tree height at the end of the second year $= 292.5$ cm.

